OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGary Lineker to return as  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMatch of the Day host      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Gary Lineker will return to present    
OL,6, Match of the Day after he was taken off
OL,7, air following an impartiality row in   
OL,8, which he criticised the government's   
OL,9, new asylum policy.                     
OL,11,FBBC director general Tim Davie         
OL,12,Fannounced an independent review will be
OL,13,Fcarried out on social media guidelines.
OL,15,FLineker said he backs the review and is
OL,16,Flooking forward to getting back on air.
OL,18,FHe said the last few days had been     
OL,19,F"surreal" and thanked people for their 
OL,20,F"incredible support".                  
